Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些血 是你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你身上都是血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走? 要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八話 人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你為什麼會帶刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽了以後也會被捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望時真同學你遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就說你現在身處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就更得知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁敲側擊 你呀是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我而言是特別的 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許也有我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能答應我 不告訴任何人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜好好吃完了早飯就去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她似乎很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又給唯芳先生添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜最喜歡爸爸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血 果然很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那喝別的 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說 那東西會吃人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾和寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有鎮上的其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的錯 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我被選中要和「古物」戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒「古物」保護大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是沒事的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始 你為什麼就抱我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是認真地在問我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼奇怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是這樣的嗎 現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟也看到那些怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是怪物 是「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是執著於一些奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼叫都沒差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許…是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是簡單擦擦 果然擦不乾淨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧 我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想送你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了不是嗎 刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…時真同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想讓大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學是很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你知道就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 今天的事就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要是再有什麼事 要告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴時真同學…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想知道 關於小夜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不舒服嗎 都是我沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我只是有點暈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是您的臉色…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 血…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上的血沾到您身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親要是發生什麼事的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該如何做才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼看上去那麼難過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親若難過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒精神 即使天氣好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒精神 沒精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是礙於在我面前 所以強撐著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會「呀」「討厭」這樣尖叫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己那傷口能迅速癒合的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 問了也白問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是和誰的約定 想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你認為如果打破約定會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「打倒古物 保護大家」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打破了這個約定 會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 難得的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦開始 就不得不決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且賞勝者 罰敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你取勝 希望得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果敗了 被奪去什麼能比死還痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不能倒下 我這個樣子搬不動你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 不是這麼簡單就能想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是應該用不了多久 恐怕馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我這就洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰與獎賞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後三天 「古物」也沒有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校通知 今天要復課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隻身一人和「古物」戰鬥 傷痕纍纍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 小夜很結實的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 還是要注意身體的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八卦中出現什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算接下來要出現的「古物」是強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜一定打倒它回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像母親那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「古物」出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把它消滅 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 你臉色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...像這個情況 也打不起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是諾諾還是寧寧都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像前幾天 巡警先生也失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鎮沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直停課 感覺好久沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次見面雖然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻感覺根本沒辦法靜下心來上課
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你也帶這個來了 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有個奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好像動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個動作遲緩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐籐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不打算讓一個人逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓誰死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是浮島神社的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣小夜同學 這些全都是你殺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中


